ttps://www.loc.gov/ndnp/listawardees.html</a>.</p>\n<p>For more information on Library of Congress policies and disclaimers regarding rights and reproductions, see <a href=\"https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html\">https://www.loc.gov/homepage/legal.html</a></p>"], "score": 14.504336, "shard": "02", "shelf_id": "sn82014189, 1908-06-08, Edition 1", "site": ["chroniclingamerica"], "source_group": "ndnp/ak", "source_modified": "2000-01-01T12:00:00Z", "subject": ["skagway", "skagway (alaska)", "alaska", "united states", "newspapers"], "subject_headings": ["Skagway (Alaska)--Newspapers", "Alaska--Skagway", "United States--Alaska--Skagway"], "subjects": [{"alaska": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:alaska&fo=json"}, {"newspapers": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:newspapers&fo=json"}, {"skagway": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:skagway&fo=json"}, {"skagway (alaska)": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:skagway+%28alaska%29&fo=json"}, {"united states": "https://www.loc.gov/search/?fa=subject:united+states&fo=json"}], "timestamp": "2024-05-22T15:22:24.542Z", "title": "The daily Alaskan (Skagway, Alaska), June 8, 1908", "type": ["issue"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn82014189/1908-06-08/ed-1/"}, "locations": null, "method": "mets_filesec", "more_like_this": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn82014189/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn82014189", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/61cdf494-77a6-53fb-a563-250f2605d792"], "batch": ["ak_bluewhale_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1904", "description": ["Triweekly, July 31, 1919-July 31, 1924 Vol. 7, no. 25 (Mar. 1, 1904)-28th year, no. 222 (July 31, 1924). Publisher: L.S. Keller, <January 2, 1912-September 30, 1913>. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:11.046Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-02", 